{"tid":758991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被捕警員數目急升　警行動處處長：痛心、辜負社會信任","createTime":"2018-07-28T07:56:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T12:46:25.000Z","uid":5195,"like":83,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"c617caf518eaeefcf36cc8a65022bf009d8b5b2a","tid":758991,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:56:55.000Z","msg":"警方早前公布今年上半年罪案數字，其中有24名警務人員被捕，當中18名涉及刑事案件，5名涉及非刑事案件如交通案件，另外有1名被其他執法部門拘捕；整體數字較上年同期增加11人或逾八成。警務處行動處處長鄧炳強今早出席電台節目時回應稱，任何人都要守法，特別是警務人員更加要潔身自愛，對於有個別同事涉及不守法而被捕的行為，他個人表示很心痛，鄧炳強又說：「他們的做法對於其他全部盡忠職守的同事，辜負了我們的期望，也辜負了社會對我們的信任，及其家人對他們的信任。」<br />\n<br />\n毅進仔今次又會唔會Diu 7 處長<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5541dd49a3856e1922d7350786fbeb51348a7f58","tid":758991,"uid":693,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T08:07:57.000Z","msg":"你地冇做錯.jpg"},{"pid":"45aeaf404a191e2ed85c4f5f9e4c10d992a34734","tid":758991,"uid":54681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T08:14:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dee622f81d7dbc13727a1a1c34f04aa7b314cd8","tid":758991,"uid":164913,"like":5,"dislike":29,"score":-24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T08:25:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5bbc0570613c9ca91ea30a712fa6fa298a73ed79","tid":758991,"uid":63853,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T08:31:28.000Z","msg":"痛心咋? 唔係震怒咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4514f0d78b9e9c991ce46378c422a502eaedc0d3","tid":758991,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T08:47:21.000Z","msg":"痛咩心？<br />\n警察 = 無做錯 = 除暴安良 = 正義"},{"pid":"03284304bb761cada1d6a24b12c5fb3d561161e9","tid":758991,"uid":54337,"like":12,"dislike":1,"sco